				<td>Add <code>"i18n":{ "msgboxHeader": "Avertissement de sortie"}</code> to the <code>data-wb-exitscript</code> attribute.</td>
				<td>Your custom message box title</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><code>exitMsg</code></td>
				<td>Show custom message</td>
